Thank you to those who responded to my post for interest in reusable fabric masks.
I have put together a small run of well built, 3-layered masks and can now offer a limited number of pre-made masks as well as accept orders beyond this.

As mentioned in my earlier post, I will be somewhat limited by my son's weekly chemo at Starship but I will give you an upfront indication of a time frame that we can make work for us bothüòä If you're able to work with me on that I'll make sure you get a well made made mask by someone who wears them a lot üëç

My intention is to make comfortable masks in order to reduce the number of times the wearer feels the urge to touch or adjust the mask, or‚Ä¶

I gave a letter to the postman,

Bright and early next morning,

We had a quarrel, a lover's spat
I write I'm sorry but my letter keeps coming back.
So then I dropped it in the mailbox
And sent it special D.
Bright and early next morning
It came right back to me.
She wrote upon it:
Return to sender, address unknown.
No such person, no such zone.‚Ä¶
